body:
Features and Enhancements

Create a List
  • Network Participation - Specialty Detail report: This a major new report which will allow users to see the exact specialty listed in each network. Each entry will be tagged with participating, or "Par", labels.
    • PLS - Par this Location AND Specialty
    • PL - Par this location but under another specialty
    • PS - Par with this specialty but at another location
    • P - Par another location and another specialty
    • N - Non-Par

Issues Fixed

Competitive Access
  • Updated breadcrumbs on the Competitive Access Reports to mirror the action items that other pages have.
    • e.g. Home > Measure Access > Competitive Access Analysis Results
  • Changed "Employees" to "Members" on all Competitive Access reports
  • Various improvements to support new browser versions, better error handling
